## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="94fc2-102">Die Spracherkennungs-Plattforminfrastruktur entpackt, die XML-basierte Struktur der SSML-Eingabe und Konstrukte <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> Objekte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94fc2-102">The Speech platform infrastructure unpacks the XML based structure of the SSML input and constructs <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> objects.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="94fc2-103">Sprachinhalt steht über den <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextLength%2A>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextOffset%2A>, und <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A> Eigenschaften eine <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> Instanz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94fc2-103">Speech content is available through the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextLength%2A>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextOffset%2A>, and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A> properties of a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instance.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="94fc2-104">Sprach-Attributinformationen, wie z. B. Hervorhebung, und Rollen Geschwindigkeit aus abgerufen werden die <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState> zurückgegebenes Objekt der <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> Eigenschaft.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94fc2-104">Speech attribute information, such as emphasis, pitch, and rate, are obtained from the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState> object returned by the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
